SQL: SELECT river.traverse FROM river,state WHERE river.traverse=state.state_name GROUP BY state.state_name ORDER BY count(river.river_name) DESC LIMIT 1 ;

Question: what cities in texas have the highest populations
SQL: SELECT city.city_name FROM city WHERE city.state_name='texas' AND city.population=(SELECT max(city.population) FROM city WHERE city.state_name='texas');
